def: A slender marine fish of the genus Ammodytes, especiallyAmmodytes tobianus of the English coast; -- called also sand lance.

Destitute of worth; having no value, virtue, excellence,dignity, or the like; undeserving; valueless; useless; vile; mean;as, a worthless garment; a worthless ship; a worthless man or woman;a worthless magistrate.'T is a worthless world to win or lose.
